# Mental Health Tracker UML

This UML file is aligned to the current frontend branch split and responsibilities for the React side of the capstone project, including `App.jsx`, the check-in form, dashboard, AI suggestion card, resource alert card, disclaimer banner, and `api.js` service layer.

---

## Frontend UML

```mermaid
classDiagram
    class App {
        +render()
    }

    class DailyCheckInForm {
        -moodScore: number
        -stressLevel: number
        -sleepQuality: string
        -journalNotes: string
        -triggers: string
        -copingStrategiesUsed: string
        +handleInputChange()
        +validateForm()
        +handleSubmit()
    }

    class MoodTrendsDashboard {
        -checkIns: CheckIn[]
        +fetchCheckIns()
        +formatMoodData()
        +formatStressData()
        +renderMoodChart()
        +renderStressChart()
    }

    class AiSuggestionCard {
        -label: string
        -suggestion: string
        +render()
    }

    class ResourceAlertCard {
        -message: string
        -resourceLinks: string[]
        +render()
    }

    class DisclaimerBanner {
        +render()
    }

    class ApiService {
        +submitCheckIn(data)
        +getCheckIns()
        +getAiRecommendation()
        +getSupportResources()
    }

    class CheckIn {
        +id: number
        +moodScore: number
        +stressLevel: number
        +sleepQuality: string
        +journalNotes: string
        +triggers: string
        +copingStrategiesUsed: string
        +createdAt: Date
    }

    App --> DailyCheckInForm
    App --> MoodTrendsDashboard
    App --> DisclaimerBanner
    DailyCheckInForm --> ApiService
    MoodTrendsDashboard --> ApiService
    DailyCheckInForm --> AiSuggestionCard
    DailyCheckInForm --> ResourceAlertCard
    DailyCheckInForm --> CheckIn
    MoodTrendsDashboard --> CheckIn
